{"type":"message","id":"f9cfa76a","parentId":"f950081e","timestamp":"2026-04-04T03:25:54.608Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 我这边还看不到你“已经创建成功”的明确信号。\n\n目前我只知道工作区里写了一个意图：  \n- clawCast 想在 `09:00-19:00` 按 `3` 的频率跑\n\n但这更像是“计划/提醒”，不等于定时任务已经真正落地了。\n\n如果你要，我现在可以继续帮你查两件事里的其中一个：\n1. **查配置文件**里有没有真的配上 cron/heartbeat  \n2. **直接检查 OpenClaw 当前运行状态**，看定时任务是否已注册\n\n你回我一句：\n- **“查配置”**\n- 或 **“直接检查”**\n\n我就继续。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0095e63be4cba3a70169d084bf52d881969e2585bff01dc83a\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":23517,"output":165,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":23682,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775273149523}}
