{"type":"message","id":"fccdeb48","parentId":"ac43aed4","timestamp":"2026-04-04T03:26:23.194Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_KK284DGsZcwOQpYyNvlzPA3B|fc_0095e63be4cba3a70169d084de754081968d7108a6f4e0dcc0","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/PLAN_MODE.md"},"partialJson":"{\"path\":\"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/PLAN_MODE.md\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":196,"output":34,"cacheRead":23552,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":23782,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775273180617}}
{"type":"message","id":"61f67172","parentId":"fccdeb48","timestamp":"2026-04-04T03:26:23.205Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_KK284DGsZcwOQpYyNvlzPA3B|fc_0095e63be4cba3a70169d084de754081968d7108a6f4e0dcc0","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# PLAN_MODE.md\n\nUse plan mode for non-trivial tasks before doing meaningful execution.\n\n## When to Enter Plan Mode\n- Multi-step tasks with dependencies\n- Anything likely to touch multiple files or systems\n- Debugging where the cause is not yet clear\n- Risky or costly actions\n- Tasks with branching options or tradeoffs\n- Any request where \"just start doing stuff\" would create thrash\n\n## What a Good Plan Looks Like\nKeep it short but concrete.\n\n### Minimum structure\n- Goal\n- Constraints / risks\n- Steps\n- First action\n\n### Example\n- Goal: verify whether a plugin is really healthy\n- Constraints: Docker socket access may be blocked; process name may not exist\n- Steps:\n  1. Check status/load state\n  2. Run functional verification\n  3. Inspect gaps if verification fails\n- First action: run status and a small roundtrip test\n\n## Execution Rules\n- Planning is not stalling. Keep it concise.\n- After planning, move into execution unless the task clearly requires confirmation first.\n- If new evidence invalidates the plan, revise it instead of pretending the old plan still fits.\n- For long tasks, checkpoint after major steps.\n- Update `WORKSTATE.md` when the plan meaningfully changes or work is interrupted.\n\n## When Not to Use Plan Mode\n- Simple factual questions\n- Single low-risk reads/checks\n- Tiny one-file edits with obvious intent\n- Cases where planning would be longer than doing\n\n## Output Style\nFor most tasks, 3–6 bullets is enough.\nDo not write a giant roadmap unless the user asked for one.\n\n## Relationship to Other Files\n- Use `RISK_TIERS.md` to judge caution level\n- Use `DIAGNOSTICS.md` for health/status investigations\n- Use `CHECKPOINTS.md` for long-running work snapshots\n- Use `WORKSTATE.md` to preserve current active state\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775273183202}}
{"type":"message","id":"5a0ab49d","parentId":"61f67172","timestamp":"2026-04-04T03:26:27.064Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"先看配置文件里有没有真的把定时任务写进去。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0095e63be4cba3a70169d084e087f8819689cda79ed3efffab\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_K6SHT3t1zZMRvoV0GSVpXry7|fc_0095e63be4cba3a70169d084e10be481968a7ca5babc1a1a85","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"find /vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace -maxdepth 3 \\( -name 'openclaw.json' -o -name 'openclaw*.json' -o -name '*.cron*' -o -name '*schedule*' -o -name '*heartbeat*' \\) -print","workdir":"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace","yieldMs":10000},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"find /vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace -maxdepth 3 \\\\( -name 'openclaw.json' -o -name 'openclaw*.json' -o -name '*.cron*' -o -name '*schedule*' -o -name '*heartbeat*' \\\\) -print\",\"workdir\":\"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace\",\"yieldMs\":10000}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":510,"output":130,"cacheRead":23680,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":24320,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775273183205}}
