{"type":"message","id":"df0f697f","parentId":"5d22a31b","timestamp":"2026-04-04T03:26:43.575Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 查到了，**有配置**。\n\n你现在的 `openclaw.json` 里已经写了 heartbeat 定时配置，大意是：\n\n- **频率**：每 **3 小时** 一次\n- **生效时段**：**09:00 - 19:00**\n- **时区**：**Asia/Shanghai**\n- **目标**：`last`\n- **直聊策略**：`allow`\n\n也就是配置层面看，**你想要的定时任务已经写进去了**。\n\n关键配置在这里：\n- `agents.defaults.heartbeat.every = \"3h\"`\n- `agents.defaults.heartbeat.activeHours.start = \"09:00\"`\n- `agents.defaults.heartbeat.activeHours.end = \"19:00\"`\n- `agents.defaults.heartbeat.activeHours.timezone = \"Asia/Shanghai\"`\n\n不过我也得说清楚一点：\n\n- **“写进配置” ≠ “现在一定正在正常触发”**\n- 要确认有没有真正注册并运行，还得再查 **OpenClaw 当前运行状态**\n\n如果你愿意，我下一步可以直接帮你查：\n**“配置有了，但实际有没有跑起来。”**\n\n你回我一句：**直接检查运行状态**。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0095e63be4cba3a70169d084ee772081968c703b920f04ccba\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":1756,"output":269,"cacheRead":24448,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":26473,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775273197035}}
{"type":"message","id":"051549f4","parentId":"df0f697f","timestamp":"2026-04-04T06:05:48.277Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"openclaw-weixin:1775282746847-5cce6ac5\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-04-04 11:37 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\n我现在飞牛openclaw面板不能修改配置文件，"}],"timestamp":1775282748266}}
{"type":"message","id":"886c2872","parentId":"051549f4","timestamp":"2026-04-04T06:05:55.509Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 那就对上了。\n\n你的情况大概率是：\n\n- **底层配置文件里已经有 heartbeat 配置**\n- 但 **飞牛里的 OpenClaw 面板目前不支持直接改这个配置**\n- 所以你会看到“面板改不了”，但实际 `openclaw.json` 已经存在对应项\n\n也就是说，**不是没配上，而是面板没有提供这个编辑入口**。\n\n你现在有两个现实选项：\n\n1. **继续用配置文件方式维护**\n   - 直接改 `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json`\n   - 适合已经能进系统文件的人\n\n2. **等面板后续支持**\n   - 如果飞牛那边未来把 heartbeat/cron 做成可视化项，就能直接在面板改\n\n如果你愿意，我可以下一步继续帮你做两件事之一：\n\n- **帮你确认这份配置是否已经生效**\n- **告诉你以后要改“频率 / 时间段 / 提示词”该改哪几行**\n\n如果你只是想知道“面板为什么改不了”，答案就是：\n\n**因为现在飞牛 OpenClaw 面板还没覆盖这部分配置能力，只能靠配置文件。**","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0095e63be4cba3a70169d0aa3e4a608196877f324a406cc394\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":26553,"output":274,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":26827,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775282748278}}
