{"type":"message","id":"667668c2","parentId":"b9f6039a","timestamp":"2026-04-04T10:12:12.147Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 有，我搜到了。\n\n## 直接相关的\n### 1. **`baidu-ocr`**\n- 名称：**Baidu Ocr**\n- 这是你要找的最直接候选\n\n---\n\n## 另外还搜到一批 OCR 相关 skills\n如果你后面想比较方案，也可以看这些：\n\n- `pdf-ocr`\n- `ocr-space`\n- `screenshot-ocr`\n- `china-doc-ocr`\n- `tencentcloud-ocr`\n- `ucloud-deepseek-ocr`\n- `image-ocr-reader`\n- `vision-recognition-ocr`\n- `ocr-local`\n- `rapid-ocr`\n- `fast-ocr`\n- `general-ocr-struct`\n\n---\n\n## 对你现在最有价值的判断\n如果你的目标是：\n\n**“接入百度 OCR”**\n\n那第一优先应该先看：\n- **`baidu-ocr`**\n\n如果你的目标是：\n\n**“先把本地 OCR 跑起来，不想立刻配 API”**\n\n那值得先看：\n- `ocr-local`\n- `rapid-ocr`\n- `pdf-ocr`\n\n---\n\n## 我建议下一步\n我可以继续帮你做两件事之一：\n\n1. **查看 `baidu-ocr` 这个 skill 的说明**\n   - 看它需要什么 API、怎么配置、适不适合你\n2. **把几个 OCR skill 横向比较**\n   - 百度 OCR\n   - 本地 OCR\n   - PDF OCR\n   - 哪个最适合你的飞牛 OpenClaw\n\n你回我一句：\n- **查看 baidu-ocr**\n- 或 **帮我比较 OCR skills**","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0095e63be4cba3a70169d0e3f3957c8196a94e12ea9380c0d8\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":662,"output":363,"cacheRead":79360,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":80385,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775297519919}}
