{"type":"message","id":"6686c14d","parentId":"84ff4cba","timestamp":"2026-04-04T17:43:33.125Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\"url\":\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/I6GDBHM7dhkvplbf99CgxA\",\"extractMode\":\"markdown\",\"maxChars\":12000}","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0fa7a480a15a5a980169d14dc22350819792deed83bd525f18\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 还没完全读完，但我已经开始抓了。  \n这篇是微信文章链接，我这边现在需要先把页面内容取出来；有些公众号页会比较慢，或者抽取不完整。\n\n你要的话我可以接着给你两种服务：\n\n1. **先给你一个快速摘要**\n2. **继续深读后给你详细拆解**\n\n如果你愿意，我现在就继续按“详细拆解”走。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0fa7a480a15a5a980169d14dc2e5b88197a6457672717fda4b\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":217,"output":150,"cacheRead":41088,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":41455,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775324607613}}
